# Static archive of GameCon 1999 (reconstructed from the Internet Archive).
#
# GameCon 1999 ran in OLOMOUC. It was a SECTION of the whole altar.cz publisher
# site (path altar.cz/gamecon/), the same path-era as 1998/2000-2005 — older
# than the gamecon.altar.cz subdomain (2006-2008).
#
# IMPORTANT — this is a MINIMAL, honest archive. Wayback never preserved a
# distinct GameCon 1999 HOMEPAGE (the site was one continuously-overwritten
# Altar section; the only early homepage snapshot is the 1998 one). What
# genuinely survives, and is served here:
#   - the Mistrovství v DrD + tournament RESULTS: vysledky99 (real 1999 results,
#     from a 2001 capture) + vysledky98,
#   - a period-correct Altar-layout homepage built to match the 1998 capture's
#     structure, pointing at the 1999 results and the previous year.
# The 1999 program/tournament pages were never published/captured — they 404.
#
# Pages restored from web.archive.org, transcoded WINDOWS-1250 -> UTF-8 (with an
# injected <meta charset>; the source declared charset only via the HTTP header).
# Dead ad embeds (Mr.Lin(x), billboard.cz) stripped. Dynamic CGI -> themed 404.

DirectoryIndex index.html
ErrorDocument 404 /404.html

Options -Indexes

<IfModule mod_rewrite.c>
    RewriteEngine On

    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} -f
    RewriteRule ^ - [L]

    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} -d
    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME}/index.html -f
    RewriteRule ^ - [L]

    RewriteRule ^$  index.html [L]

    RewriteRule ^.*$ - [R=404,L]
</IfModule>
